1
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:13,100
Okarin?

2
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:14,180
Cum?

3
00:00:16,780 --> 00:00:17,890
Cum?

4
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:24,210
Ești aici. Chiar ești aici.

5
00:00:27,490 --> 00:00:29,130
Nu ești fantomă?

6
00:00:29,299 --> 00:00:31,620
Vrei să sun la poliție?

7
00:00:31,620 --> 00:00:33,640
Vreau doar să știu adevărul!

8
00:00:33,640 --> 00:00:35,640
